Enable Minimize on clicK :gsettings set org.gnome.shell.extensions.dash-to-dock click-action 'minimize'
------------------------- gsettings reset org.gnome.shell.extensions.dash-to-dock click-action
                          gsettings set org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences button-layout ':close,maximize,minimize' 

to change icon tab:  open dconf editor --> /org/gnom/shell/extension/dash-to-dock/ and turn on show-apps-at-top
